df <- read.csv('Data/data_train_2.csv',row.names = 1)
head(df)
model <- glm(data = df, class ~ .-trestbps+log(trestbps)-chol+log(chol)-slope+poly(slope,2)-cp+factor(ca)
             -ca, family='binomial')
# extract the model summary
summary(model)
